  "notes": "Fiscal year 2020 (ended March 31, 2020). Financial statements prepared under Canadian Public Sector Accounting Standards (PSAS). Auditor is Deloitte S.E.N.C.R.L./s.r.l. (Quebec City office). The statements include additional SAC-required reporting schedules not required under PSAS. Revenues and expenses are presented gross before inter-project recharges of $9,106,261. The nation has equity-method government business enterprises (quote-part in results = $173,808; dividends received = $509,990). Contributions receivable spiked significantly from $4.7M to $11.8M. Bank borrowing increased from $5.4M to $10.9M. Large CHSLD construction project ($8.9M revenue, deferred to next year). Remuneration schedule referenced but not included in extracted text - amounts set to 0. OSR calculated as total revenue $43,608,932 minus estimated government transfers of $35,786,743. ISC (SAC) funding calculated as sum of SAC Budget de base + Pr\u00e9-\u00e9tabli + Souple + PDEA = $19,940,040. Total government transfers include all federal and provincial funding lines."
